title: Top 13.5 Hollow Knight cameos in other media
author: mossbag
description:
Hollow Knight has made cameos in a number games and media. In this video, we will take a deep dive into some other games that reference Hollow Knight.

Check out the indie games mentioned in this video:

Dead Cells
https://store.steampowered.com/app/588650/Dead_Cells/
Bug Fables
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1082710/Bug_Fables_The_Everlasting_Sapling/
Guacamelee! 2
https://store.steampowered.com/app/534550/Guacamelee_2/
The Binding Of Isaac Rebirth
https://store.steampowered.com/app/250900/The_Binding_of_Isaac_Rebirth/
Forager
https://store.steampowered.com/app/751780/Forager/
Grime
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1123050/GRIME/
F.I.S.T. Forged In Shadow Torch
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1330470/FIST_Forged_In_Shadow_Torch/
Dandara
https://store.steampowered.com/app/612390/Dandara_Trials_of_Fear_Edition/
The Adventure Pals
https://store.steampowered.com/app/396710/The_Adventure_Pals/
One Step From Eden
https://store.steampowered.com/app/960690/One_Step_From_Eden/
